title: MoneyPak cards
extract: MoneyPak is a convenient way for friends and family members to reload eligible prepaid cards. Just purchase a MoneyPak at a store near you and visit MoneyPak.com to reload a card. MoneyPak cannot be used to pay bills, fund online accounts, or add money to PayPal. To add money to PayPal, check out PayPal Cash.
